    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Transfer the <strong>softened aubergine</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
