    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, re-boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> canned lentils</strong></p>",
