    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>ground cinnamon</strong> and cook for 30 sec</p>\n<p>Return the <strong>softened aubergine</strong> to the pan and add the <strong>drained lentils</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook until step 7</p>",
