    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with 30g<span class=\"text-danger\"> [60g]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p>\n<p>Once melted, add 30g<span class=\"text-danger\"> [60g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min until a sandy paste forms – this is your<strong> roux</strong></p>\n<p>Gradually whisk 350ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> into the<strong> roux</strong>, a little at a time and cook for 5-7 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p>\n<p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>béchamel sauce</strong></p>",
