      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> aubergine &amp; lentil mix</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p>\n<p>Top with the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> then pour the<strong> béchamel sauce</strong> all over</p>\n<p>Grate the<strong> cheddar cheese</strong> all over and top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p>\n<p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min until bubbling and golden</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> parsley</strong> roughly</p>",
